{"tid":1179791,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【華為危機】英國EE開通5G服務 BBC首次5G直播用華為設備  =英國普遍支持中國大陸？？？","createTime":"2019-05-31T10:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-31T11:11:27.000Z","uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7b6498ee23e5ccef0bd4234a0dd05978e415057a","tid":1179791,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T10:51:00.000Z","msg":"英國電訊公司EE周四正式在倫敦、卡迪夫（Cardiff）、愛丁堡（Edinburgh）、貝爾法斯特（Belfast）、伯明罕（Birmingham）和曼徹斯特（Manchester）共6個城市，開通5G服務，部份5G設備使用中國科技巨擘華為的產品。有BBC記者在twitter上發帖，分享他在準備用5G直播的幕後花絮，清晰拍到有華為標誌的路由器，有女記者舉起「大拇指」。<br />\n<br />\nBBC科技節目主持人Rory Cellan-Jones在Twitter上傳一段影片並說：「它支援了我們進行BBC首次5G電視直播。」影片中，拍攝工作人員正在調較設備，車頂上放置一個有華為標誌的路由器。<br />\n<br />\nEE今年將於另外10個城市，推出5G服務，包括布里斯托（Bristol）、考文垂（Coventry）、格拉斯哥（Glasgow）、侯城（Hull City）、列斯（Leeds）、李斯特（Leicester）、利物浦（Liverpool）、紐卡素（Newcastle）、諾定咸（Nottingham）以及錫菲（Sheffield）。<br />\n<br />\nApple news"},{"pid":"d67f90c0723458eb903f8bf975f1d31557a17247","tid":1179791,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T10:51:23.000Z","msg":"【華為危機】英國EE開通5G服務 BBC首次5G直播用華為設備<br />\n <a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190531&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59661862\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190531%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59661862&d=1iSEM%2BOqawym%2FMRHoWlZoKix4Ji0%2BaXPUR6dcaOs6Zo%3D&h=254977a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190531%26s%3D10793096%26a%3D59661862&h=0c26273b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190531&amp;s=10793096&amp;a=59661862</a>"},{"pid":"875a9da95a904f585521a4356f870d733f4e56aa","tid":1179791,"uid":31637,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-31T10:54:07.000Z","msg":"屌你, 今次英國真係無撚柒用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57d7697ddfd813f4176d40a50b352d30ed157159","tid":1179791,"uid":66669,"